Created:
- src/providers/gitlab.rs: Full GitLabProvider implementing Provider trait
  - Proprietary GitLab Chat API format (NOT OpenAI-compatible)
  - POST to /api/v4/chat/completions with {content, additional_context}
  - Non-streaming: returns TextDelta + Done events from single response
  - Self-hosted base URL support (default: gitlab.com)
  - Bearer token auth (GITLAB_TOKEN / GITLAB_API_KEY)
  - 9 unit tests (defaults, builder, URL, request building, response deser)

Modified:
- src/providers/mod.rs: Added NativeGitlab variant, resolve_provider_route case, factory match arm
- tests/provider_backward_lock.rs: Added factory_routes_gitlab_native_provider test

Test results:
- 9/9 gitlab unit tests pass
- 2/2 factory dispatch tests pass
- 152/152 provider streaming tests pass (no regressions)
- cargo check --lib passes clean
- clippy clean for gitlab.rs (remaining errors are in bedrock.rs/copilot.rs from other agents)","created_at":"2026-02-10T08:35:09Z"}]}
